<H1>GGI - interface to libggi.</H1>
This package, made by Sebastian Guenther, contains the header translations
of the GGI (General Graphic Interface) library. (See their <A
HREF="http://www.ggi-project.org/">homepage</A>). It consists of units that
are straight translations of the libraries header files.

The following units are part of this package:
<UL>
<LI> <B>ggi</B> The main graphics unit.
(<A HREF="http://www.freepascal.org/docs-html/packages/ggi/ggi/">View
interface</A>).
<LI> <B>gii</B> This unit provides input handling. 
(<A HREF="http://www.freepascal.org/docs-html/packages/ggi/gii/">View
interface</A>).
<LI> <B>ggi2d</B> This unit provides procedures for drawing 2D objects.
(<A HREF="http://www.freepascal.org/docs-html/packages/ggi/ggi2d/">view
interface</A>)

</UL>
And the following example programs exist:
<UL>
<li><b>ggi1</b> A simple demonstration program.
</UL>
